    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and cut your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Cut your <strong>potato[es] </strong>(skin on) into small, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-mustard-sausage-and-apple-salad/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>onion wedges</strong>, <strong>chopped potato</strong> and<strong> sausages</strong> to a large baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4 or more? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 20-25 min or until the sausages and potatoes are golden</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-mustard-sausage-and-apple-salad/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>, <strong>honey</strong> and<strong> cider vinegar</strong> in a large bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, a splash of <strong>cold water </strong>and a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>honey mustard dressing</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-mustard-sausage-and-apple-salad/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Tear your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Once the sausages are golden, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the<strong> torn ciabatta</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 6-8 min or until the ciabatta is golden and crisp and the sausages are cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-mustard-sausage-and-apple-salad/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, cut your <strong>apple[s]</strong> (skin on) into matchsticks</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-mustard-sausage-and-apple-salad/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> salad</strong>, <strong>apple matchsticks</strong>, <strong>croutons</strong>,<strong> roast potato </strong>and <strong>roasted onion </strong>to the bowl with the <strong>honey mustard dressing</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>honey mustard & apple salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-mustard-sausage-and-apple-salad/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once done, cut each<strong> cooked sausage</strong> into 3 pieces on the diagonal</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-mustard-sausage-and-apple-salad/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> chopped sausages</strong> over the <strong>honey mustard & apple salad</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
